                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9359" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1399</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1355 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“无”到“有”：A电商公司货源模式转型之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From “None” to “Stock”: An e-commerce company sourcing model transformation road</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张雪娇，万润钰，韩玉玲，赵青扬，乔玉洋</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A电商公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购供应部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购内部控制；货源模式；电商；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Procurement internal control; Sourcing model; E-commerce</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">因无货源模式具备零库存、低成本等优势，不少投资者选择在各大电商平台开设无货源店铺，但因供货渠道无法保障、商品质量参差不齐、消费者权益易受损等原因，近年来，各大电商平台通过下架商品、缴纳违约金、关闭店铺等方式逐步加大了对无货源店铺的管控力度，敦促其构建高质量货源以实现转型。基于这一现实背景，本案例以A电商公司从“无货源模式”转型为“有货源模式”中因“无”生“难”、从“无”到“有”、从“有”到“优”的三个阶段为故事线，讲述了无货源模式导致的采购困境、有货源模式的构建策略及有货源模式下的内控优化方案。本案例旨在加深学员对采购内部控制的理解，引导学员思考在严管无货源店铺的浪潮下电商企业如何转型以破解货源模式带来的采购困局，同时有助于为其他无货源店铺的转型及营造依规有序的电商环境提供有益借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Abusive dropshipping is attractive to prospective e-commerce sellers due to its zero-inventory requirement and minimal operational costs. However, dropshipping abuse as a business model is fraught with significant issues, including unreliable supply chains, variable product quality, and a heightened risk to consumer rights. In response, major e-commerce platforms have escalated their regulatory measures against such practices by deleting listings, levying fines for infractions, and closing offending stores. These actions compel abusive dropshippers to secure dependable sources of goods, thus catalyzing a fundamental transformation in their business models. This case study explores the journey of an e-commerce company as it shifts from an abusive dropshipping model to a stock-based model. It is structured into three phases: identifying the problems inherent in the initial model, devising strategies for establishing a stock-based system, and refining the procurement process under this new regime. This case is crafted to deepen students’ understanding of internal purchasing controls and to inspire them to consider how abusive dropshippers can adapt and transform under the pressure of increasingly stringent regulatory measures to effectively tackle the procurement challenges they face. Moreover, this case provides a valuable reference for other abusive dropshippers seeking to reform their business model, thereby promoting a more regulated and orderly e-commerce ecosystem.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制与风险管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采购与付款业务流程；采购与付款内控风险；采购与付款内控风险管控措施；采购流程再造</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
